#--------------------------------------------------------
#----------------A number of scripts to handle grading
#----------------in Blackboard: obtain rosters & assignments,
#----------------enter missed work, obtain metrics on discussion
#----------------boards and reflections

#---------------------------------------------------------------

#------------------v0.52 has:
#-----------'bboard_init' to obtain roster and assignment list from gradebook csv
#-----------'work_missing' to enter in work into gradebook that is not completed
#-----------'Dboard' and 'Reflections2' to obtain metrics on student performance in discussion/reflection forums
#-----------'dboard2' integrates roster/assignment list with dboard data



#------------------v0.52+ needs:
#-----------integrate roster/assignment data into reflections
#-----------integrate Dboard & reflections directly into an uploader sheet
#-----------same for assignments:  type comments right in!
